description: It's been a very long time, but now he's back! Leo Fox has returned for more and this time he's taken a liking to the pain and torment. As he pleads and begs, Sebastian Kane has the poor boy strung up by the wrists and tied down to the floor. It's not long before Leo struggles at the mere pleasure of being pegged. Brought to the point of no return as Sebastian provokes him to shoot his load -the toned twink is left exhausted and relieved.
title: Leo Foxx & Sebastian Kane
